Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.15,0:24:48.88,Default,,0,0,50,,If you're a man, let's put your strength to test{男だったら　力を試せ}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.88,0:24:52.90,Default,,0,0,50,,If you are a man, keep your hopes sizzling{男だったら　希望(のぞみ)を燃やせ}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.90,0:24:57.26,Default,,0,0,50,,If you are a man, don't lose your heart{男だったら　くじけるな}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.26,0:25:05.83,Default,,0,0,50,,Because there's just you and me, a man and a man{俺もおまえも　男と男}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.83,0:25:14.06,Default,,0,0,50,,With crimson blood flowing in our veins all the same{おなじ真赤な　血が通う}
